  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Preoperative anxiety is a complex clinical concept with both physiological and psychological
      consequences.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This study looks at the need for a more user friendly, rapid tool for measuring preoperative
      anxiety, specifically by evaluating the visual smileys scale.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
